<h1 id="toc5"><span>混沌分裂者</span></h1>
<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://imgur.com/SKo2KxY.png" style="width:25%;" alt="SKo2KxY.png" class="image" /></div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
