<p>&quot;Hush now. I am Nobody. You can call me that.&quot;<br />
&quot;Is that your name，or not your name?&quot;<br />
&quot;I don't think there is much a difference.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p>- <a class="newpage" href="/all-words-are-lies">All Words Are Lies</a></p>
