<h1 id="toc24"><span>相啸魔</span></h1>
<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://topia.wdfiles.com/local--files/goisandyou/pattern_screamer_ball_v2.png" style="width:15%;" alt="pattern_screamer_ball_v2.png" class="image" /></div>
